🔄 6. Flow Example (Sale)
User creates sale in POS
Save sale + items
Reduce stock
Create transaction:
Entry 1: Debit Cash
Entry 2: Credit Sales
Entry 3: Debit COGS
Entry 4: Credit Inventory

